                      <locus target="#11v #17v #75r #95r #107r" facs="013 019 076 096 108">11v, 17v, 75r, 95r, 107r, </locus> (dotted line using alternating black and red);
                      <locus target="#75r" facs="076">75r</locus> (additional drawing in black and red)
                    </decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2">
                        <desc>
                           <locus target="#110r" facs="111">Fol. 110r</locus>Drawing of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5684JesusCh">Jesus Christ</persName> in black and red, with uplifted hands and an unfinished head</desc>
